body:
A unique code is created in the blockchain. A corresponding Funkopop is created.

&amp;#x200B;

With a vNFT, or TPC, what you have is a key that verifies with the Pop's unique code on the blockchain. Funkopop will honor any valid keys with their tangible counterparts. You trust the blockchain that the NFT is real, then you trust Funko to have the Pop. 

&amp;#x200B;

When you redeem the FNKO, the token is exhausted. No one will honor that token for it's Pop anymore and they can be sold separately.
